parameters: I wonder if I should clean the toilet?
\n<Mister>What will you do? Have a pee sex?
We had pee sex in the toilet...

\n<Eury>...If there's a presence behind us, let's run away
immediately.
\n<Streamer>Hello-con-chin! It's the standard greeting for Tengatsu TV!

\n<Streamer>You know, Tengatsu City is still recovering from monster
damage, and the atmosphere is a bit gloomy, right?

\n<Streamer>So, using this streaming room to deliver fun programs is my
job!
\n<Streamer>New girl! Would you like to make a guest appearance?

\n<Streamer>If new girl appears, I bet the concurrent viewers will
increase too!

\n<Streamer>No worries! I'll lead the way, and since you're cute, new
girl, you're sure to be popular!
\n<Eury>Cute!? Popular!? Do you really think so~?♪

\n<Eury>(Lifting the spirits of Tengatsu City... for the
reconstruction... Yes, this is part of my mission too!)
\n<Streamer>So, what do you say? Wanna give it a try?

\n<Streamer>That's the spirit, good rating! Let me know when you can
make an appearance!

\n<Eury>(I thought coming here would be nothing but trouble... but
maybe I've found something unexpectedly fun?)

\n<Streamer>Well then, for today, let's wrap up with an "otsunpo tsun
tsun"♪
\n<Eury>Yes, nice to meet you! Um, what kind of building is this?

\n<Owner>(...She doesn't know, even though she's a sexaroid? Is she
serious?)
\n<Owner>It's a facility where you can have sex with sexaroids.
\n<Owner>(...I see. Maybe it's still not the time for that.)

\n<Owner>Very well. Then, could I ask you to handle the reception for
a while?

\n<Owner>The thing is, people's hearts have become too rough, and
while customers come, there's no one to work.
\n<Owner>I'd prefer if you could also work as a hostess.

\n<Owner>(...A new model sexaroid with emotions. She's a bit hard to
handle.)

\n<Owner>Please come by when you have time. We're always short on
hands here.

\n<Eury>If there's anything you'd like to ask of a modified girl,
please feel free!
\n<Master>Would you like to work at my tavern, if it's okay with you?

\n<Master>I'm sure having a new model girl around would definitely
bring in more customers! Please, I'm asking you!

\n<Eury>(Hehe♪ Using the novelty of a new model modified girl to
increase the number of visitors, huh?)

\n<Eury>(It's a bit different from my usual work as a modified girl,
but if my popularity can help liven up the town even a
little, that would be great♪)
\n<Master>Oh, that's great to hear! Then I'm counting on you.

\n<Master>I know you're busy, Eury-chan, so just come and work
whenever you can. That's fine by me.

\n<Eury>(Working at the tavern... I often get called clumsy by Dr.
Marion, but I wonder if I'll be okay?)

\n<Eury>(...No, I'm not clumsy! Because I am a modified girl after
all!)

\n<Eury>I, the modified girl Eury, have successfully completed my
mission in this town!
\n<Eury>Everyone in Tengatsu Town, thank you so much for everything!
\n<Townspeople>(Though we're the ones who should be thanking you...)
\n<Townspeople>(So we can't have sex with Eury-chan anymore...)
\n<Townspeople>(I want to do it just one more time before the end!)
\n<Master>Ah, um... I have something I want to ask you.
\n<Mister>Indeed... You kept insisting, "I am not a sexaroid!"
\n<Apprentice>After all, you were strong enough to defeat monsters.

\n<Streamer>So what's the deal? Is the modified girl thing just a
setting, or is it for real? Tell us.

\n<Brothel Client>Eh, but if you were in the brothel, that means you are a
sexaroid, right?

\n<Owner>If a human was working in a brothel, that would be a
violation of the law, right?

\n<Tavern Patron>Eh, we had sex with a normal human!? Does that make us
rapists!?
\n<Brothel Employee>Hehehe... This is turning into a dangerous conversation.

\n<Eury>(If I weren't a sexaroid, all these people would be
criminals...)
\n<Eury>A new model sexaroid capable of fighting monsters!!!

\n<Owner>I see, so the modified girl was just part of the setting
after all.
\n<Thug>You came to save both the town and our dicks.

\n<Eury>Everyone, I must go to the next stronghold to defeat the
monsters.
\n<Eury>If it's okay with you, and if you didn't dislike it...
\n<Eury>I would like to do it with all of you one last time.
